# Development setup

create virtual env

```shell
python3.10 -m venv ./venv
. ./venv/bin/activate
```

install dependencies

```shell
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

install the cli

```shell
make install
```

test with

```shell
um get pods
```

## Publishing pip release

```shell
make publish
```
